the pdp lab the pdp lab people projects pdp resources about the pdp lab the pdp or parallel distributed processing lab is located in the stanford psychology department we study all aspects of human cognition through behavioral and neuroscience experiments and neural network modelling for more information about who we are please see people to see what we re working on see projects the pdptool matlab based neural network simulator and the associated pdp handbook are resources we maintain for everyone who is interested in using understanding pdp models and using them for human cognitive science and cognitive neuroscience research read an introductory article about pdptool from the matlab digest stanford home psychology dept home contact
